description: Kanade is the executive director and founder of Miyagami Private Academy, president of the Best Student Council, and the successor to the Jinguuji conglomerate. She takes a special interest in Rino and takes care of her, later found to be at the request of Rino`s mother, a relative of hers. She is able to telepathically communicate with other people.
name: Jinguuji Kanade
